| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7101 — Mass File Rename (killsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: e19164c3-5b4e-5b0a-8459-d98e8c6ef478"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
